rs of Paradise flow, and above is the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/16\/tahlil-takbir-expiate-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":42135,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Declaring glory of Allah expiates sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no one on earth who declares there is no God but Allah, Allah is the greatest, and there is no movement or might except in Allah, but that it will expiate his sins\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2699,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/imam-care-people-needs\/","url_meta":{"origin":42135,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Imam: Muslim leaders must take care of people\u2019s needs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn Murrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no leader who closes the door to someone in need, in hardship, and\u00a0in poverty, but that Allah closes the gates of heaven to him when he is in need, in hardship, and\u00a0in poverty.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.ab